                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18360201-472-offence-1 t18360201-cd-67"></join>13th of July</rs>, 1 pair of trowsers, value 18<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18360201-name-514" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-514" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18360201-name-514" type="surname" value="WATSON"></interp>
